<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Dec 2021 10:47:29 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>KIA 全新 Sportage 登場，配全景弧形液晶顯示屏</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/03/kia-sportage/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=kia-sportage</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 03 Dec 2021 10:47:29 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Kia Sportage]]></category><category><![CDATA[KIA SUV]]></category><category><![CDATA[SUV]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1074240</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日舉行香港汽車博覽 IMXHK2021 有不少車廠展出新車，而錦龍汽車就在場中展出全新的 KIA SUV 車 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近日舉行香港汽車博覽 IMXHK2021 有不少車廠展出新車，而錦龍汽車就在場中展出全新的 KIA SUV 車款 Sportage。Sportage 設計一如以 KIA 以往的設計哲學，走實用性和運動性路線，但外型上與以往 Sportage SUV 改進不少。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074242 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113912-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新 Sportage 的外觀設計上創新，線條上鮮明，造型上頗引人注目，加上簡約而富有肌肉感的車身設計與複雜的圖形互相結合，為這部 SUV 賦予更多動感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1074243 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114018-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車頭設計則以 KIA 標誌性的「虎鼻」黑色格柵為主，橫跨整個車頭前方，新設計的標誌亦新鮮感十足。細節以「回力鏢」形 LED 日間行車燈及矩陣式頭燈作點綴，為車頭外觀劃下明確的分界線。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074244 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113925-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>官方稱，為歷代 Sportage 的高實用性和運動型致敬，全新 Sportage 的兩側輪廓線條刻意營造出一種道路感，加上肌肉線條橫跨車身兩旁，將車身無縫地連接著。新設計的鍍鉻腰線連接到車尾及 D 柱，更與後擾流板形成和諧線條，進一步加強運動感。剃刀式尾燈通過細長的水平設計，賦予全新 Sportage 一個寬闊的視覺效果；富肌肉感的揭背設計，使整個車尾外觀更一體化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074245 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114026-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074246 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_114000-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>駕駛席中央配置了一體式全景「弧形液晶顯示屏」，纖薄的輕觸式屏幕和儀錶板與出風口互相襯托。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074247 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113947-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新 Sportage 採用品牌全新開發的 N3 車架結構，每個細節元素均重新設計和研發。新車架讓駕駛者充分體會 Sportage 動態操控，配合新一代電控懸掛系統，可提高駕乘品質。</p><p>第 5 代全新 Sportage 是同級車系中最安全的車輛之一，配備一系列安全設備，包括 360 全景泊車鏡頭、盲點防撞警告、盲點監控影像系統、後方交通防撞主動煞車輔助系統和後方來車防撞安全警示系統等，這些輔助駕駛系統（ADAS）大大減低意外風險。動力系統方面，Sportage 搭載全新四缸 2.0「SmartStream」MPI 氣油引擎，輸出馬力 156 匹和扭力 192 牛頓米。新 Sportage 配備 6 前速自動波箱及多種駕駛模式選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074248 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211201_113940-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 Sportage 共提供 2 個版本，分別是 Spotrage Premium 和 Sportage X-Line。售價分別是 HK$299,900 和 HK$329,900。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074249 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/image005-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/image005-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/image005-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/image005-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/image005.jpg 1299w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></p><div class="feedflare">
